     <div type="to_the_reader">
   <pb facs="16"/>
   <head>To the Reader.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>HArke Reader, would'st be learn'd ith' W<gap reason="illegible" resp="#tech" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap>rres,</l>
      <l>A Captaine in a Gowne?</l>
      <l>
         <gap reason="illegible" resp="#tech" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap>trike a league with Bookes and Scarres?</l>
      <l>And weare of both the Crowne?</l>
   </lg>
   <lg>
      <l>
         <gap reason="illegible" resp="#tech" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap>ouldst be a Wonder? such a one</l>
      <l>As could winne with a Looke?</l>
      <l>A Schollar in a Garrison?</l>
      <l>And conquer by the Booke?</l>
   </lg>
   <lg>
      <l>
         <gap reason="illegible" resp="#tech" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap>ake then this Mathematick Shield▪</l>
      <l>And henceforth by its Rules,</l>
      <l>
         <gap reason="illegible" resp="#tech" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap>e able to dispute ith Field,</l>
      <l>And combate in the Schooles.</l>
   </lg>
   <lg>
      <l>
         <gap reason="illegible" resp="#tech" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap>hil'st peacefull Learnin g once agen,</l>
      <l>And th' Souldier do concorde,</l>
      <l>As that he fights now with her Penne</l>
      <l>And shee writes with his Sword.</l>
   </lg>
   <closer>
      <signed>RICH. LOV<gap reason="illegible" resp="#tech" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap>LAC<gap reason="illegible" resp="#tech" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap>.
A. Glouces: Oxen.</signed>
   </closer>
</div>
